Global Food Grade Baking Soda Market Insights
Food Grade Baking Soda Market size was valued at USD 0.99 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.49 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Food Grade Baking Soda Market Overview
The global food grade baking soda market was valued at approximately USD 1.8 billion in 2024, with an expected growth rate of 5.6% CAGR over the forecast period (2025-2030). The market's expansion is driven by its wide application across the food and beverage industry, primarily as a leavening agent and a versatile ingredient in culinary and cleaning uses. Its role in food safety, health benefits, and sustainability is enhancing its appeal among manufacturers and consumers alike. As the demand for natural and organic food products rises, food grade baking soda is becoming increasingly important in the production of clean label foods and other applications that focus on non-toxic, eco-friendly alternatives.

